512
00:31:15,346 --> 00:31:16,687
Worse, they get bored.

513
00:31:18,107 --> 00:31:20,528
You could just break it up by having lots of small choices, of course.

514
00:31:20,828 --> 00:31:21,629
Plenty of games do this.

515
00:31:22,029 --> 00:31:22,869
Long explanation.

516
00:31:22,989 --> 00:31:23,310
Pause.

517
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,290
But, Hero, what do you think of that?

518
00:31:25,671 --> 00:31:26,711
This is bad, too.

519
00:31:26,771 --> 00:31:30,313
